1)Push(Commit) - If new push Server has to decide cluster number. And replicate. Success message.
	If already existing DB - Acquire Lock - If successful Find the cluster number - Replicate - Success Message
						If unsuccessful Retry Message



2)Pull - New request -> Find cluster number - Verify Credential -If credential is Correct - Return The Database


3)Login , Logout , Signup , GrantAccess , RevokeAccess



Database: Cluster Management - clusterNo -> DB
			       	cluster -> ServerIP List
          Credential Management- Username -> Password
			          Username -> DB

initialisation(during installation):
    runfile(database_create)


