		DecideClusterNumber(DBName) -> RoundRobinFashion
		FindClusterNumber(DBName) -> FromDatabase
		AcquireLock(DBName)
		ReplicateAndMakeConsistent(clusterNumber,DBName) -> Depends on Indexfile As well.
	
	Logout(username , Password)
	
	

